  * Added libgdal linking:
  	+ debian/control: added libgdal1-dev build-dep
        + debian/rules: added --with-gdal
   (closes: #234275)
  * Added gdal-bin as suggested (closes: #220861)
  * Now managing correctly manpages. Upstream provides preformatted ones, now
    using rman to reconvert to nroff sources.
    (closes: #216293, #159379)

